{
  "title": "Climate Change 6",
  "publicationStatus": "draft",
  "subtitle": "The Effect of Albedo",
  "helpOnLoad": true,
  "about": ["Albedo describes how much sunlight is reflected back into space without being absorbed by the surface. Albedo varies greatly depending on the type of surface the sunlight hits. In this model, you can change the amount of ice covering the surface. Graphs show temperature change, relative amounts of carbon dioxide in the atmosphere and ocean, and the amount of water vapor in the atmosphere.",
  "",
  "*This climate model cannot accurately predict Earth's future temperature or greenhouse gas levels.*"
  ],
  "theme": "has",
  "aspectRatio": 1.6,
  "fontScale": 0.7,
  "models": [
    {
      "type": "iframe-model",
      "id": "iframe-model",
      "url": "models/lab-version/1/iframe-model/iframe-model.json",
      "modelOptions":{
        "url": "//models-resources.concord.org/agentscript/global-climate/lab-embeddable.html#ocean=true",
        "animRate": 60,
        "showGases": true,
        "showRays": true,
        "showHeat": true,
        "nCO2Emission": 0.7,
        "icePercent": 0.1
      },
      "viewOptions": {
        "controlButtons": "play_reset"
      }
    }
  ],
  "outputs": [
    {
      "name": "year",
      "label": "Year",
      "format": "d",
      "unitName": "Year",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('year');"
    },
    {
      "name": "temperatureChange",
      "label": "Temperature Change",
      "format": "3.1f",
      "unitName": "degrees Celsius",
      "unitAbbreviation": "°C",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('temperatureChange');"
    },
    {
      "name": "airCO2Concentration",
      "label": "AIr CO₂ Concentration",
      "format": "3.0f",
      "unitName": "",
      "unitAbbreviation": "",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('airCO2Concentration');"
    },
    {
      "name": "oceanCO2Concentration",
      "label": "Ocean CO₂ Concentration",
      "format": "3.0f",
      "unitName": "",
      "unitAbbreviation": "",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('oceanCO2Concentration');"
    },
    {
      "name": "vaporConcentration",
      "label": "Vapor Concentration",
      "format": "3.0f",
      "unitName": "",
      "unitAbbreviation": "",
      "value": "return iframeOutput('vaporConcentration');"
    }
  ],
  "helpTips": [
    {
      "component": "",
      "text": [
        "#How do I use this model?",
        "---",
        "The temperature slider changes the average global temperature, affecting both the atmospheric and oceanic temperatures.",
        "",
        "Change the temperature, and watch the graphs to see what happens to the amount of carbon dioxide in the ocean and atmosphere.",
        "Make sure that you wait long enough to see the effect.",
        "",
        "You can hover over the controls for more information. Click to close this window."
      ],
      "showcase": true
    },
    {
      "component": [
        "temperatureGraph",
        "co2Graph"
      ],
      "text": [
        "These graphs show the relative change in temperature (upper graph) and concentration of greenhouse gases in the atmosphere and ocean (lower graph).",
        "Together these graphs show the relationship between the concentration of greenhouse gases and the temperature of the planet.",
        "---",
        "Note: This model is a simplified representation of the climate system, and as such,",
        "it does not show the actual concentrations of greenhouse gases in the atmosphere and ocean."
      ],
      "showcase": false
    }
  ],
  "components": [
    {
      "id": "temperatureGraph",
      "type": "graph",
      "resetAxesOnReset": true,
      "enableAutoScaleButton": true,
      "enableAxisScaling": true,
      "autoScaleX": true,
      "autoScaleY": true,
      "enableSelectionButton": false,
      "clearSelectionOnLeavingSelectMode": false,
      "enableDrawButton": false,
      "drawProperty": null,
      "markAllDataPoints": false,
      "showRulersOnSelection": false,
      "fontScaleRelativeToParent": true,
      "properties": [
        "temperatureChange"
      ],
      "xProperty": "year",
      "title": "Temperature Change",
      "lineWidth": 2,
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "100%",
      "xlabel": "Time (year)",
      "xmin": 2014,
      "xmax": 2022,
      "ylabel": "Temperature (°C)",
      "ymin": -12,
      "ymax": 12,
      "xTickCount": 4,
      "yTickCount": 5,
      "xscaleExponent": 0.5,
      "yscaleExponent": 0.5,
      "xFormatter": "d",
      "yFormatter": ".2r",
      "lines": true,
      "bars": false,
      "tooltip": "",
      "dataColors": [
        "#ff0000",
        "#0000ff"
      ],
      "legendLabels": [
      	"Air temperature"
      ],
      "legendVisible": true,
      "syncXAxis": "co2Graph",
      "syncYAxis": false,
      "helpIcon": true
    },
    {
      "id": "co2Graph",
      "type": "graph",
      "resetAxesOnReset": true,
      "enableAutoScaleButton": true,
      "enableAxisScaling": true,
      "autoScaleX": true,
      "autoScaleY": true,
      "enableSelectionButton": false,
      "clearSelectionOnLeavingSelectMode": false,
      "enableDrawButton": false,
      "drawProperty": null,
      "markAllDataPoints": false,
      "showRulersOnSelection": false,
      "fontScaleRelativeToParent": true,
      "properties": [
        "airCO2Concentration",
        "oceanCO2Concentration",
        "vaporConcentration"
      ],
      "xProperty": "year",
      "title": "Greenhouse Gas Concentration",
      "lineWidth": 2,
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "100%",
      "xlabel": "Time (year)",
      "xmin": 2014,
      "xmax": 2022,
      "ylabel": "Concentration",
      "ymin": 0,
      "ymax": 30,
      "xTickCount": 4,
      "yTickCount": 5,
      "xscaleExponent": 0.5,
      "yscaleExponent": 0.5,
      "xFormatter": "d",
      "yFormatter": ".2r",
      "lines": true,
      "bars": false,
      "tooltip": "",
      "dataColors": [
        "#009966",
        "#0000ff",
        "#000000"
      ],
      "legendLabels": [
      	"CO₂ in Atmosphere",
        "CO₂ in Ocean",
        "Water Vapor in Atmosphere"
      ],
      "legendVisible": true,
      "syncXAxis": "temperatureGraph",
      "syncYAxis": false
    },
    {
      "id": "speedSlider",
      "type": "slider",
      "min": 20,
      "max": 60,
      "steps": 10,
      "title": "Simulation speed",
      "labels": [
        {
          "value": 20,
          "label": "slow"
        },
        {
          "value": 60,
          "label": "fast"
        }
      ],
      "width": "9em",
      "height": "auto",
      "property": "animRate",
      "retainProperty": true,
      "disabled": false,
      "tooltip": "Change the speed of the model."
    },
    {
      "id": "iceSlider",
      "type": "slider",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 1,
      "steps": 100,
      "title": "Ice cover",
      "labels": [
        {
          "value": 0,
          "label": "0%"
        },
        {
          "value": 1,
          "label": "100%"
        }
      ],
      "width": "21em",
      "height": "auto",
      "property": "icePercent",
      "retainProperty": true,
      "disabled": false,
      "tooltip": "Change the amount of ice cover in the model."
    },
    {
      "id": "showLabel",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Show:",
      "width": "auto",
      "height": "auto",
      "tooltip": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "showGasesCheckbox",
      "type": "checkbox",
      "text": "Gases",
      "textOn": "right",
      "width": "auto",
      "height": "auto",
      "property": "showGases",
      "retainProperty": true,
      "disabled": false,
      "tooltip": "Toggle showing gases in the model."
    },
    {
      "id": "showRaysCheckbox",
      "type": "checkbox",
      "text": "Rays",
      "textOn": "right",
      "width": "auto",
      "height": "auto",
      "property": "showRays",
      "retainProperty": true,
      "disabled": false,
      "tooltip": "Toggle showing radiation in the model."
    },
    {
      "id": "showHeatCheckbox",
      "type": "checkbox",
      "text": "Heat",
      "textOn": "right",
      "width": "auto",
      "height": "auto",
      "property": "showHeat",
      "retainProperty": true,
      "disabled": false,
      "tooltip": "Toggle showing heat in the model."
    }
  ],
  "layout": {
    "rightTop": [
      "temperatureGraph"
    ],
    "rightBottom": [
      "co2Graph"
    ],
    "bottomLeft": [
      ["iceSlider"],
      ["speedSlider"]
    ],
    "bottomMiddle": [
      "showLabel"
    ],
    "bottomRight": [
      ["showGasesCheckbox"],
      ["showRaysCheckbox"],
      ["showHeatCheckbox"]
    ]
  },
  "template": [
    {
      "id": "rightTop",
      "left": "model.right",
      "width": "0.7 * model.width",
      "height": "0.5 * interactive.height",
      "padding-bottom": "1em",
      "padding-left": "0.5em"
    },
    {
      "id": "rightBottom",
      "left": "model.right",
      "top": "rightTop.bottom",
      "width": "0.7 * model.width",
      "height": "0.5 * interactive.height",
      "padding-left": "0.5em"
    },
    {
      "id": "bottomLeft",
      "top": "model.bottom",
      "left": "model.left"
    },
    {
      "id": "bottomRight",
      "top": "model.bottom",
      "right": "model.right"
    },
    {
      "id": "bottomMiddle",
      "top": "model.bottom",
      "right": "bottomRight.left",
      "padding-top": "0.2em",
      "padding-right": "0.2em"
    }
  ]
}
